House Resolution 694
By: Representatives Dickey of the 134th and Ballard of the 147th
A RESOLUTION
1 Commending Sheriff Terry Deese upon his retirement from the Peach County Sheriff's
2 Department; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, Sheriff Terry Deese has served with honor and distinction at the Peach County
4 Sheriff's Office since 1983, serving as Sheriff since 2004; and
5 WHEREAS, he is an honest and dedicated public servant who strives for excellence in all
6 of his endeavors and whose primary concern is the welfare and safety of the citizens of Peach
7 County; and
8 WHEREAS, he is highly regarded by the citizens of his community and by state and local
9 government officials as a man of unquestioned integrity and dedication to the administration
10 of justice and sound principles of law enforcement; and
11 WHEREAS, this spirited law enforcement professional has exhibited extraordinary devotion
12 to duty, outstanding loyalty, fine leadership, and meticulous attention to detail in all of his
13 duties; and
